snippet.title: Gamma Ray - Last Before The Storm (Cover)
snippet.description:
It has been more than 10 years since I opened my YouTube account, and finally today I reached 10,000 subscribers. Thanks for your supports!

During my high school days, Helloween and Gamma Ray were always on my playlist. 
It may be an unfamiliar band for young metal fans, but this is one of the bands that have led me to become a metalhead with their overwhelming intense power, and I believe their songs need to be rediscovered. 

Kai Hansen is known as one of the best guitarist and best songwriter in the metal scene. But I respect him because of the way he delivers his energy through his voice. On this song you can see his true charisma. This is the version we made as a tribute to his greatness and I hope this version reaches out Kai!
